data.title: Hammer-in anchor H2
data.meta_description: Universal hammer-in anchor with steel nail for fixing of External Thermal Insulation Composite Systems with rendering. ► Learn more.
data.text:
Technical specifications

Anchor diameter: 8 mm

Washer diameter: 60 mm

Drill hole depth h1 ≥ 35 mm (55mm)

Embedment depth hef ≥ 25 mm (45 mm)

Point thermal transmittance λ 0.001 W/K

Use categories ETA* A, B, C, D

Values in parentheses: anchoring in aerated concrete (use category E) *Specification according to ÖNorm B 6124 for concrete, solid brick and vertical brick
